videos.headline: Clemson forces fumble and recovers for TD
videos.description: LB Tre Lamar jars the ball free and DE Clelin Ferrell jumps on it in the end zone to give the Tigers a 7-0 lead.

videos.headline: Lawrence throws 17-yard TD pass to double Clemson's lead
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence throws on the move and delivers a touchdown strike to WR Hunter Renfrow, making it 14-0 Tigers.

videos.headline: Lawrence goes deep for 53-yard TD pass
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence finds a wide-open Justyn Ross, who takes it the distance and extends the Tigers' lead.

videos.headline: Lawrence picked off by Georgia Tech lineman
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence inadvertently throws it off the back of his offensive lineman, and DL Desmond Branch ends up with the interception for the Yellow Jackets,

videos.headline: Georgia Tech gets on board with 11-yard QB run
videos.description: TaQuon Marshall keeps in himself and cuts into Clemson's lead with an 11-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Clemson uses shovel pass to strike before halftime
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence completes a shovel pass to RB Travis Etienne, who battles across the goal line and scores with just seconds remaining in the first half.

videos.headline: Clemson opens second half with 27-yard TD run
videos.description: RB Tavien Feaster bursts through a hole and gets to the end zone to widen the Tigers' lead over the Yellow Jackets.

videos.headline: Clemson pours it on with 3-yard TD run
videos.description: Tavien Feaster muscles his way across the goal line for his second touchdown of the third quarter.

videos.headline: Georgia Tech scores on 2-yard RB toss
videos.description: Nathan Cottrell takes the toss and gets to the edge before diving into the end zone for a Yellow Jackets touchdown.

videos.headline: Georgia Tech picks off Clemson's backup QB
videos.description: QB Chase Brice has his pass tipped and intercepted by DB Malik Rivera, who takes it up the sideline for a big return.

videos.headline: Yellow Jackets still fighting with 5-yard TD pass
videos.description: QB Tobias Oliver throws it across his body and finds a wide-open Clinton Lynch for a Georgia Tech touchdown to cut into Clemson's lead.

videos.headline: Lawrence throws 4th TD pass of game
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence fires a 30-yard dart to WR Tee Higgins, who gets to the end zone and widens Clemson's lead.
